      "content": "but that's the thing... it's not just about changing. it feels like the foundation is completely gone. the version of me that people actually valued, the one that actually mattered, is just deleted. it's like i'm a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't belong to the person i was. it feels so heavy, like there's no point in trying to rebuild something that was clearly just a lie.",
